#  1. docstop   — stop all running containers        (safe, reversible)
#  2. docremove — remove all images                  (re-pull needed)
#  3. docwipei  — force remove all images, silent    (no output)
#  4. docwipe   — stop + remove + full system prune  (⚠️  nukes volumes & networks)
